<paragraph id="91C59938A12F78A0433DF928347EA6B2" pageId="14" pageNumber="103">Material examined.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B8C42E273F786D3271A1C4237716AFC9" pageId="14" pageNumber="103">
Holotype male, in alcohol, (LA214) SWEDEN, Sm, 
<normalizedToken id="5D4B438E94EC2B12B9F6084EA93C7DF2" originalValue="Älmhults">Aelmhults</normalizedToken>
kommun, Stenbrohult, 
<normalizedToken id="40E1D2B6A9D7B7A3351D1280D3EF0C5D" originalValue="Djäknabygds">Djaeknabygds</normalizedToken>
